//Horace stays silent for a long moment before answering.//
"It's nothing. I just haven't been to Purple Town in ages."

[["You rarely talk about it. Ever meet someone famous?" ->RarelyTalk]]

//Horace lets out a puff of air and stamps his hoof once, before turning to look at you.//

Horace: "Sometimes I forgot how young you are."

[[Be insulted -> What'sThat?]]

//Horace lets out a loud whinny that you recognize as a laugh."//

Horace: "I think whatever happens, if you keep that attitude up, you'll do fine.

[[Continue. ->Finish2]]

//Horace whinies irritatedly and kneels down to sleep.//

Horace: "All I'm saying is there's no reason to brood."

[[And that you want to bottle it up. ->BottleUp]]

//You leave Horace to his thoughts and mull over what he said. It's true that you haven't ever really been anywhere, or with anyone, but your confident things will turn out alright.

You turn off the Camp-Heater and lie down to sleep. Tomorrow Purple Town awaits!//

{SceneA2.0 Jessie x Horace}

// Horace hum and the Tommies haunting song fill the silence. //

[[There must be something else for me out there.->WishA1]]
[[Goodnight.->Goodnight Horace]]

// Horace gives you long look before shaking his head, driving off a number of glowbugs.//

I apologize. That song... put me in a weird mood.

[["Want to talk about it?" ->WantToTalk?]]

//Horace stays silent for a long time before answering.//

"Look, Jessie... I'm sorry. You are a good kid. That song, just now before we reach Purple Town, it just was a bit much."

[[Apology accepted. ->ApologyAccepted]]
